Package: libghc6-haskelldb-hsql-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Suggests: haskell-haskelldb-hsql-doc (= ${source:Version})
Depends: ${haskell:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GHC6 library which gives HaskellDB support for HSQL backends
 HaskellDB is library for expressing database queries and operations
 in a type safe and declarative way. This package contains the library
 to use HDBC backends in HaskellDB5B.
 .
 HaskellDB compiles a relational algebra-like syntax into SQL, submits
 the operations to the database for processing, and returns the results
 as ordinary Haskell values.

